# Privacy Policy

**Last Updated: 2025-06-27**

We are deeply committed to the privacy and security of our users. We believe in transparency and want you to understand what information we collect, how we use it, and with whom we share it.

We believe in being transparent about security. No service is completely immune to risk, which is why our core security principle is to minimize the data we collect. The safest data is the data we never store in the first place.

Our goal is to empower you to make informed decisions about your data.

